32 superblockHash) public view returns (
        bytes32 _blocksMerkleRoot,
        uint _accumulatedWork,
        uint _timestamp,
        uint _prevTimestamp,
        bytes32 _lastHash,
        uint32 _lastBits,
        bytes32 _parentId,
        address _submitter,
        Status _status,
        uint32 _blockHeight
    ) {
        SuperblockInfo storage superblock = superblocks[superblockHash];
        return (
            superblock.blocksMerkleRoot,
            superblock.accumulatedWork,
            superblock.timestamp,
            superblock.prevTimestamp,
            superblock.lastHash,
            superblock.lastBits,
            superblock.parentId,
            superblock.submitter,
            superblock.status,
            superblock.blockHeight
        );
    }

    // @dev - Returns supe
